      <title>Republican Sen. Thom Tillis will not seek reelection next year after Trump attacks</title>
      <author>Deirdre Walsh</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/06/29/g-s1-75207/republican-thom-tillis-reelection-trump</link>
