      <title>U.N. nuclear watchdog says Iran could enrich uranium again in 'a matter of months'</title>
      <author>Joe Hernandez</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/06/29/nx-s1-5450282/u-n-nuclear-watchdog-says-iran-could-enrich-uranium-again-in-a-matter-of-months</link>
