      <title>Deadline nears for Taiwan's Chinese immigrants to prove no China household registration</title>
      <author>Ashish Valentine</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/06/29/g-s1-73842/taiwan-china-immigrants-household-registration</link>
